A '''Yunkai'i whore''' is a character in the [[Season 3|third season]]. She is played by [[Talitha Luke-Eardley]].
sections.Biography:
===Background===
She's a [[Prostitution|whore]] and [[Slavery|bedslave]] trained in [[Yunkai]].

===[[Season 3]]===
She kept the company of the [[Second Sons (mercenary company)|Second Sons]] and was used by [[Mero]] to help him, [[Prendahl na Ghezn]] and [[Daario Naharis]] decide which one of them would assassinate [[Daenerys Targaryen]].
